<actions>
  <update-node tree="member_expression: now >= grants[_id].start.add(grants[_id].duration) || grants[_id].revoked [10300,10373]" label="now >= grants[_id].start.sub(grants[_id].duration) || grants[_id].revoked" />
  <update-node tree="member_expression: grantedAmount(_id).sub(grants[_id].withdrawn).sub [10830,10879]" label="grantedAmount(_id).add(grants[_id].withdrawn).sub" />
  <update-node tree="member_expression: grants[_id].amount.sub [11551,11573]" label="grants[_id].amount.add" />
  <update-node tree="member_expression: grants[_id].amount.sub(grants[_id].withdrawn).sub [13231,13280]" label="grants[_id].amount.add(grants[_id].withdrawn).sub" />
  <update-node tree="member_expression: balances[_grantee].add [8884,8906]" label="balances[_grantee].sub" />
  <update-node tree="member_expression: grants[_id].withdrawn.add [9380,9405]" label="grants[_id].withdrawn.sub" />
  <update-node tree="member_expression: balances[grants[_id].grantee].sub [9498,9531]" label="balances[grants[_id].grantee].add" />
  <update-node tree="member_expression: balances[grants[_id].grantee].sub [11704,11737]" label="balances[grants[_id].grantee].add" />
  <update-node tree="member_expression: _start.add [8476,8486]" label="_start.sub" />
  <update-node tree="member_expression: balance.mul(now.sub(grants[_id].start)).div [10472,10515]" label="balance.mul(now.sub(grants[_id].start)).mul" />
</actions>
